dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Milwaukee County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads (2017) and right of ways (ROW) (2018) for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Milwaukee_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://county.milwaukee.gov/EN/Administrative-Services/Land-Information-Office/GIS-Data-DownloadsThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. The 'Milwaukee_Roads_2017' feature class may be considered current as of December 31, 2016, and the 'Milwaukee_ROW_2018' feature class may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
